    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "ウオッカ",
            "enName": "Vodka",
            "jpText": "やっぱウマ娘っていやぁ、\nカッコよくなきゃな！",
            "enText": "Yup, no doubt about it. \nThe best horsegirls are the cool ones!",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "pathId": -4474266613066565660,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "なーに言ってんのよ。1番に必要なのは\nカッコよさじゃなくてカワイさよ、カワイさ！",
            "enText": "What nonsense. <i>Obviously</i> cuteness trumps \ncoolness any day of the week!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "pathId": -38977368654840066,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウオッカ",
            "enName": "Vodka",
            "jpText": "はぁ？　断然カッコよさだって！",
            "enText": "What?! Are you crazy?!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "pathId": -472506483474996243,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウオッカ",
            "enName": "Vodka",
            "jpText": "この前見た……『3ハロンの恋人』だったか？\n相手の男がカッコイイ、最高って騒いでたろ！",
            "enText": "What about that movie? \"Three Furlongs of \nthe Heart,\" right? You were going on and on \nabout how cool the male lead was!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "pathId": -670883416253345050,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "ウオッカこそ！\nヒロインがカワイく成長してくの、\n思いっきり応援してたじゃない！",
            "enText": "Well, what about you?! You said the heroine \nwas so cute, you just <i>had</i> to cheer her on!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "pathId": 4046759621021038271,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウオッカ",
            "enName": "Vodka",
            "jpText": "…………。\n今回は、このくらいにしておいてやる。",
            "enText": "…You know what, let's just leave it at that.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "pathId": -3228867074934362560,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ダイワスカーレット",
            "enName": "Daiwa Scarlet",
            "jpText": "……そ、それはこっちの台詞よ！",
            "enText": "…Th-That's my line.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "pathId": -3233151050473551790,
            "blockIdx": 7
        }
    ],
